# Pre-prompt Instructions

Add your custom instructions, context, coding preferences, and guidelines here.
This file will be automatically included in every new agent session.

Example instructions you might want to add:
- Coding style preferences
- Project-specific conventions
- Important context about the codebase
- Preferred patterns or architectures
- Any specific requirements or constraints

## Feature Documentation
Anytime we make a new agent and add functionality, review if we need to update the Features file, which should include all major user-facing features in the app.
